    "description": "Are you a skilled Surgeon looking for your next big career move? Symbiosis Hospital Asia Pacific Associates in Tiruchirappalli offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Symbiosis Hospital Asia Pacific Associates:\nSymbiosis Hospital Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Maintain accurate clinical documentation in electronic health records\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in NABH Standards\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Flexible working hours\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Symbiosis Hospital Asia Pacific Associates!",
